05:18.800 --> 05:21.280
.."you never know what's going to
come down the river."

05:23.360 --> 05:24.600
And it's true.

05:26.920 --> 05:31.000
Little Ruby's fate came
a thousand miles too soon.

05:35.720 --> 05:39.880
