you a different child, Tommy.

13:29.160 --> 13:32.240
HE SIGHS
What child?

13:32.240 --> 13:33.840
ENGINE STOPS

13:33.840 --> 13:36.120
A daughter lost.

13:36.120 --> 13:37.400
A son found.

13:40.400 --> 13:42.080
Before you went to France,

13:42.080 --> 13:45.440
