16:13.360 --> 16:15.680
What is this good that you
will become?

16:18.680 --> 16:20.640
SHE BREATHES DEEPLY

16:25.880 --> 16:27.600
I killed a woman.

16:28.720 --> 16:30.720
I killed a woman and three men.

16:30.720 --> 16:33.240
