26:28.520 --> 26:29.840
Oh, goodie.

26:40.520 --> 26:41.680
Charles?

26:44.240 --> 26:45.560
I heard cars.

26:50.160 --> 26:51.520
Mr Shelby, the guests are...

26:51.520 --> 26:52.720
I know.

26:54.320 --> 26:57.800
Dad, there's a Bentley and a
Rolls-Royce.

27:00.760 --> 27:01.800
