27:03.960 --> 27:05.320
Go to bed, Charles.

27:13.280 --> 27:14.800
I can't sleep.

27:18.240 --> 27:20.080
I see her, when I shut my eyes.

27:21.840 --> 27:23.800
Go to your mum.

27:23.800 --> 27:25.880
She'll be awake.

27:25.880 --> 27:27.840
She holds on to me.

27:27.840 --> 27:29.360
Let her hold on to you.

27:30.800 --> 27:32.680
You hear me?

27:32.680 --> 27:34.160
Always let her hold on to you.

27:35.400 --> 27:36.640
Go on.

27:41.480 --> 27:44.200
Mr Shelby, the guests said they
would understand if...

27:44.200 --> 27:46.280
Have you served them drinks? Yes.

27:46.280 --> 27:47.520
Yeah.

28:00.120 --> 28:01.560
OK, Frances.

28:07.120 --> 28:08.640
The agenda is in my head.

28:10.000 --> 28:11.960
The agenda is in my head.

28:12.960 --> 28:14.200
I'm OK.

28:15.560 --> 28:16.880
