28:20.560 --> 28:22.800
If someone touches you, you won't
shatter.

28:25.360 --> 28:27.400
Sing it.

28:27.400 --> 28:29.440
Sing it. I love that song.

28:29.440 --> 28:30.480
I...

28:30.480 --> 28:33.880
