coffee.

29:47.400 --> 29:49.880
We should all remember this is
serious business.

29:59.440 --> 30:00.760
Oh, Diana.

30:03.000 --> 30:05.680
Now, look what you've done. You have
killed the mood.

30:10.840 --> 30:14.240
Let her sing her fucking song to
raise our spirits. Go on, please.

30:24.040 --> 30:28.680
they call Belfast

30:32.400 --> 30:36.800
happiness

30:36.800 --> 30:40.760
