English abound

34:31.560 --> 34:35.760
but we represent the true liberated
spirit of the country that...

34:35.760 --> 34:37.120
..populated your own.

34:39.400 --> 34:42.280
I hear about communists in both
places.

34:42.280 --> 34:44.400
We are the bulwark against them.

34:45.600 --> 34:48.480
When it comes to the working class,

34:48.480 --> 34:51.840
we could move our people from
Republicanism...

34:51.840 --> 34:53.880
